data.title: Jonathan Swift
data.meta_description: Penguin's MP - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document is an acknowledgements page from the introduction of a book about Jonathan Swift and his writings. It thanks various friends, colleagues, and institutions who provided assistance during the editing and preparation of the book. Specifically, it acknowledges help with bibliographic research, manuscript preparation, translations, fact-checking, and moral support. It also thanks libraries and collections that provided permission to reproduce images.
